{
  "texts": [
    "Fig. 8.8Fig.",
    "Astrometric calibration of KiDS DR5, with respect to Gaia DR3 stars at epoch J2000.",
    "Values here show the median astrometric residual per pointing for stars in the magnitude range 16.5 ≤ G ≤ 19.",
    "The colour bar shows the location of each field in the Dec direction, after subtracting a constant equal to the mean declination of all fields in the relevant hemisphere.",
    "Absolute residuals are typically less than the 0."
  ]
}